{"tid":505187,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"24歲青年倒卧鳳樓","createTime":"2017-12-21T00:27:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-21T00:41:29.000Z","uid":53553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ec00693dc5101d7c48cfeb83d21fc27601ba357a","tid":505187,"uid":53553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T00:27:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20171220/57607363\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171220%2F57607363&d=jR0cHZac4yDs2OhOEsM1khFQyUQXuyYblCT5RSyYNoQ%3D&h=e1bf233f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171220%2F57607363&h=90b34f49\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20171220/57607363</a> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n昨晚上8時許，警方接獲報案，指旺角亞皆老街52-54號一單位內有人自殺，警員到場拍門無人應，遂即破門入內，發現姓方24歲男子倒卧地上，身旁有一炭爐，經救援人員檢查後證實不治， <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n據悉，涉事為鳳樓單位，間有多個房間由鳳姐租用，由於有房間空置，業主作劏房出租，死者獨居一個房間。警方撿獲一張事主的地盤平安卡，但沒有發現遺書，初步調查相信事件沒有可疑，死因有待驗屍後確定。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n24小時求助熱線︰ <br />\n香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會熱線︰23892222 <br />\n撒瑪利亞會熱線(多種語言)︰28960000 <br />\n生命熱線︰23820000 <br />\n東華三院芷若園熱線︰18281 <br />\n社會福利署熱線︰23432255 <br />\n醫院管理局精神健康專線(24小時精神健康熱線諮詢服務)：24667350 <br />\n明愛向晴熱線：18288"},{"pid":"35a962f9a5eb94ea3d13c76d8c982fb25f3f0a56","tid":505187,"uid":4917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T00:41:29.000Z","msg":"建興<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}